messages.body: $ISRG Long, bullish, full, multi-year position.  This is one I hardly even check up on because it's MOAT is so dominant.  However, do want to say I *love* the venture fund.  Frankly, it should be $500M, not $100M.  ISRG has billions in cash.  They could easily offer a dividend or do another huge share buyback program, as in the past.  But VC seeding is so much better.  Another brilliant move from one of the smartest management teams out there.
